data.description: *MOTIVATED SELLER*Take a look at this adorable home located in the quiet subdivision of Belle Lagos. This newly built home sits on a corner lot, spacious backyard, and offers an open floor plan for family gatherings and entertaining, as well as a split bedroom concept. This home has been loved in and is ready for new owners to love it as well.
